list.abstract: anything，英文单词，作代词、名词、副词，翻译为任何东西、重要的事情、在任何程度上等。

《Anything.feat User and Pharrell》是Jay-Z与User和Pharrell共同演唱的一首歌曲，收录于专辑《Kingdom Come》中。 我们常说的Anything是Jay-Z独唱的一首歌曲，很多资料声称这是一首收自《Kingdom Come( Jay-Z 专辑)》的一首歌，其实这两首都叫Anything但是并不是同一首歌。这首尽管是Jay-Z独唱的歌，但是却被收进了饶舌歌手Beanie Sigel的专辑《The Truth (Beanie Sigel 专辑)》。

yingyinNormal.en: God can forgive us for anything. Really? Anything?
yingyinNormal.zh: 上帝会宽恕我们一切。真滴？任何事？

yingyinNormal.en: So Jack, anything you recognize, buddy, Jack, anything?
yingyinNormal.zh: 杰克，还能记起点什么，任何事？

yingyinNormal.en: You can do anything, go anywhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可以做任何事，去任何地方。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyone want me to appraise anything?
yingyinNormal.zh: 有人要我评价任何事物吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Sacks will do anything for his master.
yingyinNormal.zh: 萨克斯为了他的师父，会做任何事情。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll go. I'll do anything with anybody.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我去。我愿意和任何人一起做任何事。

yingyinNormal.en: You can tell us anything. We don't judge.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可以告诉我们任何事，我们不会指责你的。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm your sister. We're us. You can tell me anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是你姐姐，我们是一家人，你可以告诉我任何事。

yingyinNormal.en: I believe in you, Elsa. More than anyone or anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我信任你，艾莎，胜于任何人任何事。

yingyinNormal.en: Blu, let me tell you something. If anything, and I mean anything, ever happens to you. I'll take care of your family.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，布鲁，我告诉你。如果你出了任何事，我是指任何事，我会帮忙照顾好你的家人。

yingyinNormal.en: And I would do anything to have you back in my life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只要你回到我身边，我可以做任何事。

yingyinNormal.en: For you, and for any dear to you, I would do anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为你们，和你们关爱的人，我愿做任何事。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. You're right. I don't pay attention to anything you do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，你说得对。我对你所做的任何事都毫不留心，

yingyinNormal.en: What do you not do? Anything else. I believe we have communicated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不应该做什么？除此之外的任何事。我觉得我们已经达成共识了。

yingyinNormal.en: I need to tell you something. Anything. And I don't want you to react.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我需要告诉你一些事，任何事都行。我不希望你有什么反应.

yingyinNormal.en: Which you didn't feel obliged to share. I'm not obliged to do anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你觉得没义务分享给我。我没有义务做任何事。

yingyinNormal.en: Bowling ball and bowling ball. They're the same. It doesn't mean anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 保龄球和保龄球，它们是一样的。这不能说明任何事。

yingyinNormal.en: I suppose you'll need some help. I'm sure Teddy would do anything for you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我认为你需要一些帮助，我相信泰迪愿意为你做任何事。

yingyinNormal.en: And my mom does the most. For never giving up. On anything. Especially, me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 特别是我妈妈。因为她从不放弃任何事情，特别是我。

yingyinNormal.en: You foolish woman. You don't understand. You're not in control of anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你这愚蠢的女人，你根本不明白，你完全掌控不了任何事。

word_usage.usage:
anything主要用于疑问句、否定句或条件从句中代替something，意为“任何东西；任何事情绝对不”。例：
He didn't say anything.
他啥也没说。

anything也可用于肯定句，表示“无论什么东西；随便什么事情”。例：
I want something to eat, anything will do.
我想吃点东西，随便什么都行。

anything是复合不定代词，形容词修饰其时被形容词修饰时，形容词必须放在其后。例：
I don't have anything suitable to wear for the party. 
我没有适合在聚会上穿的衣服。

word_usage.usage:
形容词修饰复合不定代词something, anything, nothing, everything时，形容词耍位于复合不定代词之后。
如：Think of something interesting and special to write about.
想一些有趣并且特别的事情来写。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 表示“某事；某物”，通常用在肯定句中；something还可以用在表示邀请、请求或期待得到肯定回答的疑问句中。
表示“某事；某物”，通常用在否定句或疑问句中；还可以表示“任何事；任何东西”，此时可以用在肯定句中。
